WEBVTT

00:08.356 --> 00:10.532
[Screaming]

00:10.575 --> 00:12.664
Idalia: [Whispering]
Dios te salve María llena eres

00:12.708 --> 00:16.059
de gracia el señor es contigo.

00:16.103 --> 00:21.717
Bendita tú eres entre todas
las mujeres

00:21.760 --> 00:23.719
y bendito es el fruto
de tu vientre Jesús.

00:23.849 --> 00:33.729
♪

00:33.859 --> 00:35.731
[Walker growling]

00:35.861 --> 00:43.217
♪

00:43.347 --> 00:50.746
♪

00:50.876 --> 00:52.052
Do you think we'll hit
somewhere soon?

00:52.182 --> 00:54.706
I'm not trying
to think at all.

00:54.837 --> 00:56.186
Maria's still
following us.

00:56.317 --> 00:58.797
Ignore her.

00:58.928 --> 01:00.408
Are we near
the old campgrounds?

01:00.538 --> 01:03.715
♪

01:03.846 --> 01:04.977
I don't know.

01:05.108 --> 01:06.414
Are we?

01:06.544 --> 01:07.937
I may know a place.

01:08.068 --> 01:12.289
Um, but we can only
stay there for, like, a night.

01:12.420 --> 01:13.856
Who lives there?

01:13.986 --> 01:18.208
This woman, uh,
if she's still there.

01:18.339 --> 01:19.949
Well, if she's still there,
maybe she'll let us stay

01:20.080 --> 01:22.430
for more than one night,
and if she's not, well...

01:22.560 --> 01:27.217
♪

01:27.348 --> 01:28.914
What?

01:29.045 --> 01:31.091
She's, like, um...
I don't know.

01:31.221 --> 01:33.615
She has, like, an intuition.
Like, um, a healer.

01:33.745 --> 01:35.312
You know, like,
spells and stuff.

01:35.443 --> 01:38.010
Spells?

01:38.054 --> 01:40.143
Yeah, you know,
like a bruja.

01:40.274 --> 01:42.798
Is that the bad kind of witch
or the good kind?

01:42.928 --> 01:45.017
There are no bad w--
Never mind.

01:45.148 --> 01:53.330
♪

01:53.461 --> 01:55.332
I think
this is the place.

01:55.463 --> 01:57.943
-You don't know?
-Shh!

01:58.074 --> 01:59.510
I've only heard stories.

01:59.641 --> 02:02.687
♪

02:02.818 --> 02:04.515
How the hell are we supposed
to get in?

02:04.646 --> 02:08.650
♪

02:08.780 --> 02:10.304
Here.

02:10.434 --> 02:13.089
♪

02:13.220 --> 02:14.960
Good call.

02:15.091 --> 02:16.658
[Gate creaks]

02:16.788 --> 02:25.667
♪

02:25.797 --> 02:34.676
♪

02:34.806 --> 02:36.591
Eric: Crazy.
You'd barely even know

02:36.721 --> 02:38.201
there's a house
behind these walls.

02:38.332 --> 02:43.598
♪

02:48.211 --> 02:56.654
♪

02:56.698 --> 02:59.309
Old Woman: [Whispering] Ahora y
en la hora de nuestra muerte.

02:59.353 --> 03:00.615
Amén.

03:00.745 --> 03:02.094
♪

03:02.225 --> 03:05.010
[Clanging]

03:05.141 --> 03:08.057
[Chickens clucking]

03:08.188 --> 03:13.018
♪

03:22.854 --> 03:25.030
[Gasps]

03:25.161 --> 03:27.424
Sorry.

03:27.555 --> 03:33.082
♪

03:33.213 --> 03:38.740
♪

03:38.870 --> 03:41.308
Hello?

03:41.438 --> 03:42.570
Is anyone there?

03:42.700 --> 03:52.014
♪

03:52.144 --> 04:01.415
♪

04:01.545 --> 04:10.815
♪

04:10.946 --> 04:20.303
♪

04:20.434 --> 04:29.617
♪

04:29.747 --> 04:39.061
♪

04:39.191 --> 04:40.541
-Oh! Sorry.
-Jesus.

04:40.671 --> 04:42.804
Doña Alma?

04:42.934 --> 04:50.420
♪

04:50.551 --> 04:53.684
[Rustling]

04:53.815 --> 04:55.817
What the hell was that?

04:55.947 --> 04:57.079
Leave!

04:57.209 --> 04:58.950
No, please.

04:59.081 --> 05:01.518
I --
We do not want to hurt you.

05:01.649 --> 05:03.041
I used to live nearby.

05:03.172 --> 05:05.522
Nobody lives nearby.

05:05.653 --> 05:06.915
I know someone
that used to come to you

05:07.045 --> 05:09.613
for candles and tinctures.

05:09.744 --> 05:11.180
Maria?

05:11.311 --> 05:13.225
♪

05:13.356 --> 05:14.966
We -- We just need
somewhere to stay.

05:15.097 --> 05:16.968
Just for the night.

05:17.099 --> 05:19.014
Well,
you cannot stay here.

05:19.144 --> 05:20.755
♪

05:20.885 --> 05:23.758
[Speaking Spanish]

05:23.888 --> 05:29.677
♪

05:29.807 --> 05:35.639
♪

05:35.770 --> 05:38.599
[Speaking Spanish]

05:38.642 --> 05:39.687
Sí.

05:39.817 --> 05:42.298
♪

05:42.429 --> 05:43.778
Thank you.

05:43.908 --> 05:45.345
Thank you.

05:45.475 --> 05:46.955
The bathroom is there.

05:47.085 --> 05:48.173
Go wash up.

05:48.304 --> 05:50.393
Okay.
The --
The water works?

05:50.524 --> 05:58.401
♪

05:58.532 --> 06:06.540
♪

06:06.583 --> 06:08.368
Maria.
Sí.

06:08.498 --> 06:10.587
I have a hard time
believing that.

06:10.718 --> 06:17.333
♪

06:17.464 --> 06:23.992
♪

06:24.122 --> 06:26.037
She -- She said that
you were a healer

06:26.168 --> 06:27.952
and that
you could help us.

06:28.083 --> 06:34.698
♪

06:34.829 --> 06:37.658
Go wash up.

06:37.788 --> 06:39.268
Thank you.

06:39.399 --> 06:46.275
♪

06:58.113 --> 07:04.728
♪

07:04.859 --> 07:07.775
I have some spare blankets
you can take when you leave.

07:07.905 --> 07:10.473
♪

07:10.604 --> 07:13.694
Sorry,
but I just gotta ask.

07:13.824 --> 07:17.306
Why?

07:17.437 --> 07:18.960
Where are we
supposed to go?

07:19.090 --> 07:21.049
♪

07:21.179 --> 07:22.616
We came all this way.

07:22.746 --> 07:25.009
♪

07:25.140 --> 07:27.272
I'm not sure
why you did that.

07:27.403 --> 07:29.100
What are we supposed
to do tomorrow night?

07:29.231 --> 07:30.406
Or the night after?

07:30.537 --> 07:32.669
Eric...
No, it's true.

07:32.800 --> 07:34.715
It's freezing out there.

07:34.845 --> 07:37.021
We almost died.

07:37.065 --> 07:39.023
We willdie.Stop.

07:39.154 --> 07:42.766
You have all this space,
and it's just us two.

07:42.897 --> 07:44.812
We don't need much.

07:44.942 --> 07:46.988
♪

07:47.118 --> 07:50.208
No.

07:50.339 --> 07:51.819
Seriously?

07:51.949 --> 07:54.212
♪

07:54.343 --> 07:55.605
You're just gonna...

07:55.736 --> 07:58.434
You're just gonna give us
a death sentence?

07:58.565 --> 07:59.827
Hmm?

07:59.957 --> 08:02.307
We're all heading
in that direction.

08:02.438 --> 08:04.440
Yeah, well,
we don't have to yet.

08:07.356 --> 08:08.879
Váyanse.

08:08.923 --> 08:11.360
Por favor.

08:11.491 --> 08:14.058
[Sighs]

08:14.189 --> 08:22.980
♪

08:23.111 --> 08:24.068
[Slams table]

08:24.199 --> 08:25.548
[Gasping]

08:25.679 --> 08:29.117
♪

08:29.247 --> 08:30.684
[Choking]

08:30.814 --> 08:36.864
♪

08:36.994 --> 08:42.957
♪

08:43.087 --> 08:45.046
[Body thuds]

08:45.176 --> 08:53.141
♪

08:53.271 --> 09:01.279
♪

09:01.410 --> 09:09.505
♪

09:10.854 --> 09:12.813
[Sighs]

09:15.424 --> 09:23.911
♪

09:24.041 --> 09:32.484
♪

09:32.615 --> 09:41.102
♪

09:41.232 --> 09:49.676
♪

09:49.806 --> 09:50.981
[Gasps]

09:51.112 --> 09:53.549
[Choking]

09:53.680 --> 10:00.774
♪

10:00.904 --> 10:02.602
[Gasps]

10:05.822 --> 10:15.789
♪

10:23.927 --> 10:26.626
[Sighs]
A real fireplace.

10:26.756 --> 10:30.455
I mean,
this house is something.

10:30.586 --> 10:33.633
Imagine in the spring and the
summer what we could do with it.

10:35.635 --> 10:37.941
Just because she's dead,

10:38.072 --> 10:41.684
it doesn't mean
we can take this house.

10:41.815 --> 10:45.470
We're not --
We're not taking anything.

10:45.601 --> 10:47.472
She's gone.

10:47.603 --> 10:50.780
It's messed up,
but we're protected by stone.

10:50.911 --> 10:52.913
You know?
No one could hear us.

10:52.956 --> 10:55.567
No stink of
the sonámbulos.

10:55.698 --> 10:57.787
It's like a little fortress.

10:57.918 --> 11:01.922
You know, we can't just
leave it sitting here.

11:02.052 --> 11:04.272
Gotta reframe how
you're thinking about it.

11:04.402 --> 11:06.578
♪

11:06.709 --> 11:08.189
Hey, hey.

11:08.319 --> 11:11.061
♪

11:11.192 --> 11:14.021
She fell, Dali.

11:14.151 --> 11:23.030
♪

11:23.160 --> 11:27.382
Do you think she'd want to come
back as one of those things?

11:27.512 --> 11:29.253
No.

11:29.384 --> 11:31.212
It's sad, but...

11:31.342 --> 11:32.953
we've been on the run
from the dead

11:33.083 --> 11:35.999
almost as long
as we've been together.

11:36.130 --> 11:37.740
Shitty things happen now.

11:37.871 --> 11:41.918
♪

11:42.049 --> 11:46.314
So, what, does that mean
we gotta stop living?

11:46.444 --> 11:47.794
No.

11:47.924 --> 11:53.408
♪

11:53.538 --> 11:56.193
Dali, will you settle down
with me

11:56.324 --> 11:57.891
in this sick-ass house

11:58.021 --> 12:01.459
and do nothing
for forever?

12:01.590 --> 12:03.810
We could even snore
as loud as we want to.

12:03.940 --> 12:06.551
It was your snoring,
and it almost got us killed.

12:06.682 --> 12:08.118
Ah, yeah, yeah, yeah.

12:08.249 --> 12:12.732
♪

12:12.862 --> 12:14.603
Never had
a place of our own.

12:14.734 --> 12:23.830
♪

12:23.960 --> 12:33.143
♪

12:33.274 --> 12:42.457
♪

12:42.587 --> 12:51.727
♪

12:51.858 --> 13:00.954
♪

