♪

13:10.441 --> 13:19.842
♪

13:19.886 --> 13:21.931
Idalia: [Whispering]
Dios te salve María llena eres

13:21.975 --> 13:23.672
de gracia el señor es contigo.

13:23.715 --> 13:26.022
Bendita tú eres entre todas
las mujeres

13:26.066 --> 13:30.722
y bendito es el fruto
de tu vientre Jesús.

13:30.766 --> 13:32.899
La Doña: [Whispering]
Esta es mi casa.

13:36.467 --> 13:38.600
Eric, did you say something?

13:38.730 --> 13:40.123
Eric: What?

13:42.299 --> 13:44.084
Yeah, I said, "What?"

13:44.214 --> 13:51.526
♪

13:51.656 --> 13:59.055
♪

13:59.186 --> 14:01.014
Voice: [Speaking Spanish]

14:01.144 --> 14:07.890
♪

14:08.021 --> 14:14.854
♪

14:14.897 --> 14:16.464
iHola, guapo!

14:16.594 --> 14:23.601
♪

14:23.732 --> 14:25.255
Who's there?

14:25.386 --> 14:33.394
♪

14:33.524 --> 14:35.048
Hello?

14:35.178 --> 14:44.927
♪

14:45.058 --> 14:46.842
[Squawks]

14:46.973 --> 14:48.800
Wow.

14:48.931 --> 14:50.367
Hey, bud.

14:50.498 --> 14:52.195
How long you been in there?

14:52.326 --> 14:53.631
You hungry?

14:53.762 --> 14:54.850
All right.

14:54.981 --> 14:58.158
Let me see where your food is.

14:58.288 --> 14:59.289
There we go.

14:59.420 --> 15:02.510
That's fine.

15:02.640 --> 15:04.816
Okay.

15:04.947 --> 15:05.992
What's up?

15:06.122 --> 15:07.732
Here you go.

15:09.343 --> 15:12.346
That's fine.

15:12.476 --> 15:13.869
What's your name?

15:14.000 --> 15:16.959
Oh, no, wait. Don't tell me.
Let me guess.

15:17.090 --> 15:18.265
Eladio?

15:18.395 --> 15:19.962
No?

15:20.093 --> 15:21.877
It's probably Brad, then.

15:22.008 --> 15:23.139
I know.
How about you keep eating.

15:23.270 --> 15:24.924
Just tell me later, huh?

15:24.967 --> 15:26.316
Tengo frío. [Whistles]

15:26.447 --> 15:27.535
You're cold?

15:27.665 --> 15:31.234
All right.
I got you.

15:31.365 --> 15:33.280
[Squawks] Stop!
Stop!

15:33.410 --> 15:36.065
Oh, oh,
okay, okay, okay, okay.

15:38.502 --> 15:40.113
Wow.

15:42.593 --> 15:44.247
Hey, look what I found.

15:46.032 --> 15:47.207
He's cute, right?

15:47.250 --> 15:49.774
[Whistles]
iHola guapo!

15:49.905 --> 15:53.126
Do birds eat guisado?

15:53.256 --> 15:54.431
Oh, no,
you don't want it?

15:54.562 --> 15:56.085
All right.
Well...

15:59.654 --> 16:01.221
You're not that hungry,
huh?

16:01.351 --> 16:02.962
All right.
To the cage you go.

16:06.356 --> 16:08.141
[Cage door opens]

16:15.322 --> 16:18.151
This lady had --
she had everything.

16:20.849 --> 16:23.417
Yeah, she must've
known something we didn't.

16:23.547 --> 16:24.766
Well, she definitely
didn't "know"

16:24.896 --> 16:27.899
what was gonna happen
tonight.

16:28.030 --> 16:29.249
That was a joke.

16:29.379 --> 16:30.380
Awful, awful joke.

16:30.511 --> 16:31.816
I'm sorry.

16:31.947 --> 16:34.819
We have to be careful
about what we say.

16:34.950 --> 16:36.343
Because it's bad energy.

16:36.473 --> 16:39.563
Yeah, it's only bad
if you believe it's bad.

16:39.694 --> 16:41.304
That was a joke.

16:43.350 --> 16:48.659
♪

16:48.790 --> 16:50.270
You all right?

16:50.400 --> 16:55.144
♪

16:55.275 --> 16:57.625
It's just this house.

16:57.755 --> 16:59.888
How come you didn't tell me
about this place?

17:00.019 --> 17:02.630
♪

17:02.760 --> 17:06.590
Well, I mean,
I wasn't not telling you.

17:06.721 --> 17:07.939
I just...

17:08.070 --> 17:09.550
I forgot.

17:09.680 --> 17:11.073
And a lot was happening.

17:11.204 --> 17:13.771
♪

17:13.902 --> 17:17.558
You know?
We were surviving.

17:17.688 --> 17:19.212
Right.

17:19.342 --> 17:21.214
Yeah, we're surviving.

17:21.344 --> 17:24.217
Definitely gotta
remember that.

17:24.347 --> 17:25.870
Yeah.

17:26.001 --> 17:27.394
We're lucky
to have each other.

17:27.524 --> 17:30.310
♪

17:30.440 --> 17:31.659
Eric: Mm, sexy.

17:31.789 --> 17:33.400
Ew, stop.

17:37.404 --> 17:40.059
Hey. No.
What are you doing?

17:40.189 --> 17:41.625
What does it look like
I'm doing?

17:41.756 --> 17:43.105
No, Eric.

17:43.236 --> 17:44.541
This is her bed.

17:44.672 --> 17:47.066
It's just a regular mattress.

17:48.632 --> 17:50.634
Come on. The other rooms
in this house are tiny.

17:50.765 --> 17:52.767
I mean, you can go sleep
in there if you want,

17:52.897 --> 17:55.987
'cause you're tiny,
but...

17:56.118 --> 17:59.382
I don't want you to.

17:59.513 --> 18:02.298
Come on.
It's a real bed.

18:02.429 --> 18:05.780
Not even a little tempted?

18:05.910 --> 18:08.870
Come on.

18:09.000 --> 18:10.176
Yes.

18:10.306 --> 18:11.612
I want you close.

18:11.742 --> 18:14.484
♪

18:14.615 --> 18:16.965
Is your talking friend
gonna be joining us?

18:17.096 --> 18:20.447
Oh, Paco?
Nah.

18:20.577 --> 18:23.624
Paco?Yes, after my sister's dog.

18:23.754 --> 18:25.539
Aw.

18:25.669 --> 18:28.629
I hope Paco's just surviving
out there.

18:28.759 --> 18:32.328
Paco was a pug with one eye
and a fall clothing collection.

18:32.459 --> 18:34.591
There's no way.

18:34.722 --> 18:36.985
He, for sure, peaced.

18:37.116 --> 18:39.335
Mm.

18:39.466 --> 18:44.340
You know, there's a bathtub
with hot water

18:44.471 --> 18:47.517
that's big enough
for the two of us.

18:47.648 --> 18:50.303
All right, well,
I like where your head's at.

18:50.433 --> 18:53.436
♪

18:53.567 --> 18:55.308
[Water runs]Ooh! Hot!

18:55.438 --> 18:57.440
♪

