A nightmare.

21:55.096 --> 21:58.969
Yeah, but she was there --
right there -- in the wall.

22:01.015 --> 22:02.495
Right there?

22:02.625 --> 22:04.192
You sure it was Maria?

22:04.323 --> 22:07.543
Yeah.

22:07.674 --> 22:09.632
Well, it's freezing.
We should --

22:09.763 --> 22:12.505
We should go back up,
okay?

22:12.635 --> 22:14.942
I'm sorry that, uh,
I made you sleep on that bed.

22:15.072 --> 22:17.161
I know
you were uncomfortable.

22:17.292 --> 22:19.468
I'll switch it out.

22:19.599 --> 22:22.515
How are you so relaxed?

22:22.645 --> 22:25.866
'Cause I got
some good sleep.

22:25.996 --> 22:28.303
You know, how about you rest,
I'll go raid the chicken coop?

22:28.434 --> 22:30.784
Make us some eggs.

22:30.914 --> 22:32.568
All right.

22:32.699 --> 22:41.925
♪

22:42.056 --> 22:51.282
♪

22:51.413 --> 23:00.596
♪

23:00.727 --> 23:09.953
♪

