[Gasps]

23:49.645 --> 23:58.785
♪

24:33.515 --> 24:34.560
You okay?

24:34.690 --> 24:38.738
Um, I just feel...
cooped up.

24:38.868 --> 24:42.350
Like I'm waiting to be attacked
or something.

24:42.481 --> 24:43.656
You want me to
come with you?

24:43.786 --> 24:45.658
No.

24:45.788 --> 24:48.399
Fine.
I'm just trying to help.

24:48.530 --> 24:51.446
Yeah, you're always
trying to help.

24:51.577 --> 24:53.274
What does that mean?

24:59.410 --> 25:03.023
It's nothing.
I'm sorry.

25:03.153 --> 25:04.981
[Speaks Spanish]

25:06.896 --> 25:08.202
That's cute.

25:10.291 --> 25:11.597
I'm gonna
go for a walk.

25:11.727 --> 25:15.078
