27:20.551 --> 27:22.510
[Walkers snarling]

27:22.641 --> 27:31.171
♪

27:31.301 --> 27:32.520
[Gasps]
[Clucking]

27:32.651 --> 27:37.090
♪

27:37.220 --> 27:38.221
[Chuckles]

27:38.352 --> 27:39.962
[Speaks Spanish]

27:43.400 --> 27:46.534
[Parrot squawking]

27:52.496 --> 27:54.934
