28:02.768 --> 28:05.031
Can I tell you
something?

28:05.161 --> 28:08.904
Mm-hmm.

28:09.035 --> 28:11.646
I've been hearing
whispers.

28:11.777 --> 28:13.343
Whispers?

28:13.474 --> 28:18.566
Yeah.
And, uh, sometimes, um...

28:18.697 --> 28:20.089
I'll see things.

28:20.220 --> 28:22.701
♪

28:22.831 --> 28:24.528
Don't look at me
like that.

28:24.659 --> 28:27.270
