we're in her house.

28:58.954 --> 29:02.131
Eating her food.

29:02.262 --> 29:03.306
You can tell me.

29:03.437 --> 29:04.655
I want to know.

29:04.786 --> 29:06.396
Are you serious?

29:06.527 --> 29:09.182
This is our house,
Idalia.

29:09.312 --> 29:10.661
Things have changed.

29:10.792 --> 29:14.187
People take what's in front
of them. That's it.

29:14.317 --> 29:15.492
End of story.

29:15.623 --> 29:16.842
All right?

29:16.885 --> 29:18.060
Parrot: iHola guapo!
[Whistles]

29:18.191 --> 29:20.106
