30:30.306 --> 30:32.700
I th--

30:32.831 --> 30:34.441
♪

30:34.571 --> 30:36.878
I thought nothing.
Is that what you wanna hear?

30:37.009 --> 30:42.666
♪

30:42.797 --> 30:45.365
