♪

33:09.726 --> 33:16.864
♪

33:16.995 --> 33:18.909
Hello?

33:19.040 --> 33:21.260
Oh, thank God, Eric.

33:21.390 --> 33:22.565
I-Is that you?

33:22.696 --> 33:23.827
It's me, Eric.

33:23.958 --> 33:25.351
Maria.

33:25.481 --> 33:27.831
♪

33:27.962 --> 33:28.789
Maria?

33:28.919 --> 33:30.573
Let me in.

33:30.704 --> 33:33.098
I can't.

33:33.228 --> 33:34.316
You're dead.

33:34.447 --> 33:36.188
Yes, you can!

33:36.318 --> 33:41.019
♪

33:41.149 --> 33:43.325
Please just...

33:43.456 --> 33:46.502
find someplace else.

33:46.633 --> 33:48.722
You can't be serious.

33:48.852 --> 33:51.203
Somewhere else?

33:51.333 --> 33:53.901
I walked
all the way here.

33:54.032 --> 33:56.208
This is insane!

33:56.338 --> 33:58.384
Is Idalia in there?

33:58.514 --> 34:00.429
Idalia!

34:00.560 --> 34:02.170
Idalia!

34:02.301 --> 34:04.042
She did this to me.

34:04.172 --> 34:07.219
You know she did, Eric.

34:07.349 --> 34:10.352
Get her.

34:10.483 --> 34:11.962
We ca-- We can't --
We can't let you in there.

34:12.093 --> 34:15.140
Look at me, Eric.

34:15.270 --> 34:16.750
We can all share.

34:16.880 --> 34:21.494
♪

34:21.624 --> 34:23.104
We can all share.

