We should have --
No.

34:57.660 --> 34:59.009
We should've helped her.
I should've helped her.

34:59.140 --> 35:01.011
No.
I --

35:01.142 --> 35:03.884
I saw her --
I saw her down the road...

35:04.014 --> 35:05.320
Eric, look at me....on the way up here.

35:05.451 --> 35:09.237
Look at me.
Eric, she wasn't alive, okay?

35:09.368 --> 35:10.456
Do you understand?

35:10.586 --> 35:11.674
What?

35:11.718 --> 35:13.850
That was a Sonámbulo.
Okay?

35:13.981 --> 35:15.069
We're seeing things.

35:15.200 --> 35:17.724
♪

35:17.854 --> 35:20.596
No. You -- You felt --

35:20.727 --> 35:22.120
You felt her.

35:22.250 --> 35:23.730
No.
She followed us.

35:23.860 --> 35:25.384
Maria: Eric!
Let me in!

35:25.514 --> 35:27.255
You can hear her right now!
You can --

35:27.386 --> 35:30.519
Eric, no, Eric,
it's in your head, okay?

35:30.650 --> 35:31.955
We're hearing things.

35:32.086 --> 35:34.393
That was a Sonámbulo,
