35:49.495 --> 35:51.323
No, Eric,
it's in your head.

35:51.453 --> 35:53.455
I'm not seeing things,
Dali.

35:53.586 --> 35:54.935
Don't put -- Don't --
Don't put -- Stop --

35:55.065 --> 35:56.676
