trust you anymore.

36:31.406 --> 36:34.279
You can't trust me?

36:34.409 --> 36:35.584
[Groans]

36:35.715 --> 36:36.803
All right?

36:36.933 --> 36:38.587
Answer me this, huh?

36:38.718 --> 36:41.024
Answer me this.

36:41.155 --> 36:43.766
Maria?
You said that you --

36:43.810 --> 36:47.901
you ran into the Sonámbulos
looking for food with her, huh?

36:48.031 --> 36:49.337
