turn on each other.

37:23.893 --> 37:25.286
Then why'd you even
bring it up?!

37:25.417 --> 37:27.462
Because it was only supposed
to be one night!

37:27.506 --> 37:29.421
And then -- And then --
La Doña: [Whispering]
Esta es mi tierra.

37:29.551 --> 37:31.597
[Groans] Damn.

37:31.727 --> 37:34.730
Don't go. Don't --
Idalia!

37:34.861 --> 37:35.775
Maria: Idalia!

37:35.905 --> 37:37.124
Hello?

37:40.736 --> 37:42.695
