39:07.693 --> 39:16.049
♪

39:16.179 --> 39:24.579
♪

39:24.710 --> 39:28.104
Where did you -- What --
What happened?

39:28.235 --> 39:30.280
They're --
They're all down there.

39:30.411 --> 39:31.543
Who?
Everyone.

39:31.673 --> 39:32.935
Everyone
that we've ever met.

39:33.066 --> 39:36.374
Everyone that --
that you --

39:36.504 --> 39:40.203
