Idalia.

39:45.905 --> 39:48.995
That's it.

39:49.125 --> 39:50.649
Doña Alma --

39:50.779 --> 39:51.737
Doña Alma knows,

39:51.867 --> 39:53.826
and she's doing this
to us.

39:53.956 --> 39:55.610
