41:30.183 --> 41:31.837
We gotta go.
We gotta go!

41:31.967 --> 41:35.754
♪

41:35.884 --> 41:37.016
Go!

41:37.146 --> 41:42.543
♪

41:42.674 --> 41:48.070
♪

